<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Surajit Sen | Nature & Lens</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif; background: #f5f2eb; color: #2c2c2a; }
    a { text-decoration: none; }

    .page { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 0 3rem; }

    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3B6D11 0%, #639922 60%, #97C459 100%);
      padding: 3rem 2rem 2.5rem;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 0 0 20px 20px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero-leaves {
      position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
      opacity: 0.07; font-size: 80px; pointer-events: none;
      display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 20px; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    }
    .profile-ring {
      width: 110px; height: 110px; border-radius: 50%;
      border: 4px solid #C0DD97;
      background: #27500A;
      margin: 0 auto 1rem;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 36px; font-weight: 500; color: #C0DD97;
      position: relative; z-index: 1;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; color: #EAF3DE; position: relative; z-index: 1; letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
    .hero .tagline { font-size: 14px; color: #C0DD97; margin-top: 6px; position: relative; z-index: 1; letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
    .hero-badges { display: flex; gap: 8px; justify-content: center; margin-top: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    .badge { background: rgba(234,243,222,0.15); color: #EAF3DE; font-size: 12px; padding: 4px 14px; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid rgba(192,221,151,0.4); }

    nav {
      display: flex; gap: 4px; justify-content: center;
      padding: 1.2rem 1rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #d3d1c7;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      background: #f5f2eb;
      position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 10;
    }
    nav button {
      background: transparent; border: 1px solid #b4b2a9;
      color: #5f5e5a; font-size: 13px; padding: 7px 20px;
      border-radius: 20px; cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.2s; font-family: Georgia, serif;
    }
    nav button:hover, nav button.active {
      background: #639922; color: #EAF3DE; border-color: #639922;
    }

    .section { padding: 2rem 1.5rem; display: none; }
    .section.visible { display: block; }
    .section-title {
      font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #27500A;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem; padding-bottom: 8px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #639922; display: inline-block;
    }

    .about-card {
      background: #fff; border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.8rem; border: 1px solid #d3d1c7;
    }
    .about-card p {
      font-size: 15px; color: #444441; line-height: 1.9;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .about-card p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .about-highlight {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(120px, 1fr));
      gap: 12px; margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }
    .highlight-box {
      background: #EAF3DE; border: 1px solid #C0DD97;
      border-radius: 10px; padding: 1rem; text-align: center;
    }
    .highlight-box .icon { font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .highlight-box .label { font-size: 11px; color: #3B6D11; }
    .highlight-box .val { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: #27500A; margin-top: 2px; }

    .photo-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .photo-card {
      background: #fff; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid #d3d1c7; cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }
    .photo-card:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(99,153,34,0.15); }
    .photo-placeholder {
      height: 170px; display: flex; align-items: center;
      justify-content: center; font-size: 44px;
    }
    .photo-card.c1 .photo-placeholder { background: #C0DD97; }
    .photo-card.c2 .photo-placeholder { background: #D3D1C7; }
    .photo-card.c3 .photo-placeholder { background: #FAEEDA; }
    .photo-card.c4 .photo-placeholder { background: #EAF3DE; }
    .photo-card.c5 .photo-placeholder { background: #97C459; }
    .photo-card.c6 .photo-placeholder { background: #B4B2A9; }
    .photo-label { padding: 10px 14px; }
    .photo-label strong { display: block; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #27500A; margin-bottom: 2px; }
    .photo-label span { font-size: 12px; color: #888780; }

    .upload-hint {
      margin-top: 1rem; background: #EAF3DE;
      border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px 16px;
      font-size: 13px; color: #3B6D11; border: 1px solid #C0DD97;
    }

    .blog-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
    .blog-card {
      background: #fff; border: 1px solid #d3d1c7;
      border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.25rem;
      display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: flex-start;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }
    .blog-card:hover { border-color: #639922; }
    .blog-dot {
      width: 50px; height: 50px; border-radius: 10px;
      background: #EAF3DE; display: flex; align-items: center;
      justify-content: center; font-size: 24px; flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .blog-content .blog-date { font-size: 11px; color: #888780; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .blog-content h3 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: #27500A; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .blog-content p { font-size: 13px; color: #5f5e5a; line-height: 1.7; }
    .blog-tag {
      display: inline-block; font-size: 11px; padding: 3px 10px;
      border-radius: 10px; background: #EAF3DE; color: #3B6D11;
      margin-top: 8px; border: 1px solid #C0DD97;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center; padding: 2rem 1rem;
      border-top: 1px solid #d3d1c7; margin-top: 1rem;
      background: #f5f2eb;
    }
    .footer p { font-size: 12px; color: #888780; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .social-row { display: flex; gap: 10px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .social-btn {
      font-size: 13px; padding: 8px 22px; border-radius: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #b4b2a9; color: #5f5e5a;
      background: transparent; cursor: pointer;
      font-family: Georgia, serif; transition: all 0.2s;
      text-decoration: none; display: inline-block;
    }
    .social-btn:hover { background: #639922; color: #EAF3DE; border-color: #639922; }
    .social-btn.insta {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #833ab4, #fd1d1d, #fcb045);
      color: white; border: none;
    }
    .social-btn.insta:hover { opacity: 0.88; }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .hero h1 { font-size: 22px; }
      .photo-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .blog-card { flex-direction: column; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-leaves">
      <span>🌿</span><span>🍃</span><span>🌱</span><span>🌾</span><span>🍂</span>
      <span>🌿</span><span>🍃</span><span>🌱</span><span>🌾</span><span>🍂</span>
    </div>
    <div class="profile-ring">SS</div>
    <h1>Surajit Sen</h1>
    <p class="tagline">Explorer &nbsp;|&nbsp; Photographer &nbsp;|&nbsp; Storyteller</p>
    <div class="hero-badges">
      <span class="badge">Nature Lover</span>
      <span class="badge">Odisha</span>
      <span class="badge">Lens &amp; Life</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <nav>
    <button class="active" onclick="showSection('about', this)">About Me</button>
    <button onclick="showSection('photography', this)">My Photography</button>
    <button onclick="showSection('blog', this)">Blog &amp; Activities</button>
  </nav>

  <!-- ============ ABOUT ============ -->
  <div class="section visible" id="about">
    <span class="section-title">About Me</span>
    <div class="about-card">
      <p>Hello! I'm Surajit Sen, born and raised in the beautiful city of Cuttack, Odisha. I'm someone who finds peace in the rustling of leaves, the dance of morning light on still water, and the quiet stories that nature whispers to those who listen.</p>
      <p>I carry my camera everywhere — not just to capture moments, but to preserve feelings. Every photograph I take is a small tribute to the world's unnoticed beauty. This space is where I share my journeys, thoughts, and the frames I fall in love with.</p>
      <div class="about-highlight">
        <div class="highlight-box">
          <div class="icon">📍</div>
          <div class="val">Cuttack</div>
          <div class="label">Odisha, India</div>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-box">
          <div class="icon">📷</div>
          <div class="val">Nature</div>
          <div class="label">Photography</div>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-box">
          <div class="icon">✍️</div>
          <div class="val">Stories</div>
          <div class="label">Blog writer</div>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-box">
          <div class="icon">🌿</div>
          <div class="val">Explorer</div>
          <div class="label">Outdoors</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ============ PHOTOGRAPHY ============ -->
  <div class="section" id="photography">
    <span class="section-title">My Photography</span>
    <div class="photo-grid">
      <div class="photo-card c1">
        <div class="photo-placeholder">🌅</div>
        <div class="photo-label"><strong>Golden Hour</strong><span>Sunrise at the riverside</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="photo-card c2">
        <div class="photo-placeholder">🌿</div>
        <div class="photo-label"><strong>Into the Green</strong><span>Forest trails of Odisha</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="photo-card c3">
        <div class="photo-placeholder">🌊</div>
        <div class="photo-label"><strong>Still Waters</strong><span>Reflections at dusk</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="photo-card c4">
        <div class="photo-placeholder">🦋</div>
        <div class="photo-label"><strong>Tiny Worlds</strong><span>Macro nature shots</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="photo-card c5">
        <div class="photo-placeholder">🌧️</div>
        <div class="photo-label"><strong>Monsoon Magic</strong><span>Rain &amp; wet earth</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="photo-card c6">
        <div class="photo-placeholder">🌾</div>
        <div class="photo-label"><strong>Rural Frames</strong><span>Village life &amp; fields</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="upload-hint">
      💡 These are placeholder cards. Replace the emoji sections with &lt;img&gt; tags pointing to your photo URLs to show your real shots!
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ============ BLOG ============ -->
  <div class="section" id="blog">
    <span class="section-title">Blog &amp; Activities</span>
    <div class="blog-list">
      <div class="blog-card">
        <div class="blog-dot">🌄</div>
        <div class="blog-content">
          <div class="blog-date">October 2024</div>
          <h3>A morning I almost missed</h3>
          <p>Woke up at 5 AM on a whim, grabbed my camera, and headed to the Mahanadi bank. What I found there changed how I see ordinary days.</p>
          <span class="blog-tag">Nature Walk</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="blog-card">
        <div class="blog-dot">📚</div>
        <div class="blog-content">
          <div class="blog-date">September 2024</div>
          <h3>Preparing for OSSC CGL — my honest journey</h3>
          <p>Balancing exam prep with a love for the outdoors isn't easy. Here's how I'm making it work, one day at a time.</p>
          <span class="blog-tag">Personal</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="blog-card">
        <div class="blog-dot">🌿</div>
        <div class="blog-content">
          <div class="blog-date">August 2024</div>
          <h3>Bhitarkanika — where the wild breathes</h3>
          <p>A solo trip to Bhitarkanika mangrove forest. Just me, my lens, and thousands of years of untouched nature.</p>
          <span class="blog-tag">Travel</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>Made with love from Cuttack, Odisha 🌿</p>
    <div class="social-row">
      <!-- ✏️ REPLACE the href below with your actual Instagram profile URL -->
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/YOUR_USERNAME_HERE" target="_blank" class="social-btn insta">
        📸 Follow on Instagram
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<script>
  function showSection(id, btn) {
    document.querySelectorAll('.section').forEach(s => s.classList.remove('visible'));
    document.querySelectorAll('nav button').forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
    document.getElementById(id).classList.add('visible');
    btn.classList.add('active');
  }
</script>
</body>
</html>
